{"word":"G4866 - συναθλέω - synathléō - soon-ath-leh'-o - Labour with","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συναθλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synathléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-ath-leh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Labour with</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொால் - கூடப்போராடு, கூடப்பிரயாசப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to strive at the same time with another"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G118 - ἀθλέω - athléō - ath-leh'-o/118\">G118</a>; to <i>wrestle</i> in company <i>with</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>seek jointly:</i> - labour with, strive together for.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G118/118\">G118</a>, <a href=\"#/G119/119\">G119</a>, <a href=\"#/G4866/4866\">G4866</a>"}]}